Flask of Crimson Tears: A sacred flask modelled after a golden holy chalice that was once graced by
a tear of life. Though currently empty, simply rest at a site of grace to replenish. It is said that
a Finger Maiden will bestow two such chalices upon the chosen Tarnished when they meet.
