Neutralizing Boluses: Green boluses made from cave moss. Craftable item. Alleviates poison buildup
and cures poison ailment. Poison accumulates gradually, coming into effect once the threshold is
reached.
---
Stanching Boluses: Red boluses made from cave moss. Craftable item. Alleviates impending blood loss.
Take one of these in timely fashion to avoid such an event.
---
Thawfrost Boluses: Ice-hued boluses made from cave moss. Craftable item. Alleviates buildup of frost
and cures frostbite ailment.
---
Stimulating Boluses: Light-purple boluses made from cave moss. Craftable item. Alleviates buildup of
sleep. Take one of these in timely fashion to avoid such events.
---
Preserving Boluses: Scarlet boluses made of cave moss. Craftable item. Alleviates scarlet rot
buildup and cures rot aliment. Scarlet rot accumulates gradually, coming into effect once the
threshold is reached.
---
Rejuvenating Boluses: Black boluses made of cave moss. Craftable item. Alleviates death blight
buildup. Blight accumulates slowly, causing instant death once the threshold is reached. Take one of
these in timely fashion to avoid such an event.
---
Clarifying Boluses: Yellow boluses made of cave moss. Craftable item. Alleviates madness buildup.
Take one of these in timely fashion to avoid such events.
