Margit's Shackle: A fetish bathed in golden magic. Shackles were used to bind the accursed people
called the Omen, and these ones were made to keep a particular Omen under strictest confinement.
Though faint, the shackles still retain vestiges of power—enough to trap the once-bound Margit on
earth, if only for a short time.
