Kaiden Helm: Helm worn by Kaiden sellswords. These hulking, fearless mercenaries, said to hail from
the mountaintops of the wintry north, are adept at fighting on horseback. Kaiden is the name of
their home settlement.
---
Kaiden Armor: Armor worn by Kaiden sellswords. Made with the pelt of a snow-wolf, which protects
against the cold. These hulking, fearless mercenaries, said to hail from the mountaintops of the
wintry north, are adept at fighting on horseback. Kaiden is the name of their home settlement.
