Perfumer Hood: Hood of an Erdtree Capital perfumer. In times past, the role of perfumer was much
respected; a blessed apothecary in the eyes of the many. But after entering the battlefields of the
Shattering they performed no such role, trading their aromatics for poisons and explosives.
---
