Banished Knight Helm: Thick, full set of armor covering the entire body. This helm was worn by
knights who, whether by misfortune or misdeed, were forced to abandon their homes. Perhaps the deep-
red scarf was used to block the winds, for on the outskirts, the winds bite with a stinging
fierceness.
---
